longBusinessSummary: Industrial Tech Acquisitions, Inc. does not have significant operations. The company focuses on effecting a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. It intends to engage in providing 4D imaging radar solutions. The company was incorporated in 2020 and is based in Houston, Texas.
